cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image analysis and computer vision, specifically semantic boundary and edge detection. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the use of backpropagation and visualization algorithms could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
